title: Lulu - Greatest Hits Tour, Bristol Colston Hall [2004] @ 192kbps
description:
THIS IS NOT A BOOTLEG!

I didn't know the titles of all the songs featured here so I have not entered them. If you are a major LULU fan then you will obviously know what's what and perhaps you could let us know the track listing. Track 8 is 2 songs that sound better running into each other as they do so I have left them as one track.

Remember to enter the song titles in the properties also otherwise it will look crap!

Hope you like this anyway - something a little bit different for the fan who has it all.

HIGH QUALITY
